			<h1>Leadership team</h1>
<p>Andy Garner and Gordon Barrs both have over 20 years of experience as software developers working for companies such as Just Eat, Asos, Clarkes and Tesco. They founded Elastic Mint with the goal of delivering excellent software that delights users.</p>
